quote.summary: Redsun Services Group Ltd is a holding company mainly involved in the provision of property management services, value-added services to non-property owners and community value-added services. Property management services mainly provide public order, cleaning, greening, facility management, customer services and repairs and maintenance services, as well as shopping malls, home improvement and furnishings malls, hotels and theme parks. Value-added services to non-property owners cover consulting services, preliminary planning and design consultancy services, sales assistance services and other value-added services to property developers, such as inspection services. Community value-added services include property brokerage services, property decoration services, community convenience services, common area value-added services, intelligent services, retail services, assets management services and home decoration services. The Company mainly conducts its businesses in China market.
